  <summary date="2019-08-29T17:24:35Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Restoring Local Control Over Public Infrastructure Act of 2019

This bill nullifies rules issued by the Federal Communications Commission that revoke state and local authority to regulate telecommunications equipment deployment and to determine the amount of payment for the use of such equipment.</summary>
